This is a phase IV, multicenter, randomized, double blind clinical trial.

 The investigators will study 48 patients with remitting relapsing multiple sclerosis (MS) experiencing moderate or severe attack receiving immunomodulatory therapy or not.

 Patients will be randomly assigned to one of the two groups.

